Why Visualize Data?

Visualizing data should you provide more context and information than any other form of stakeholder engagement. Otherwise, dont visualize the data.

A Visualization Should be:

Effective * Delivering the facts better than any other method

Expressive * Show all the facts, and only the facts (relevant facts)
